title: New: LeyeT – Call U Out
body:
I’ve still never been to LA, however I’d be willing to bet this track from Cali newcomer **LeyeT** would likely soundtrack any trip I were to make out there.

Centred around her unique, angelic vocal, _Call U Out_ dips it’s toes into the murky EDM territories, yet manages to keep the songwriting at the centre of the track – allowing it to remain truly memorable.

Check Call U Out below, and the awesome [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/itsLeyeT/) while you’re at it.
